column1: # This file contains the network properties of the 299 diseases used in:
# Uncovering Disease-Disease Relationships Through The Human
# by Joerg Menche, Amitabh Sharma, Maksim Kitsak, Susan Dina
#    Ghiassian, Marc Vidal, Joseph Loscalzo & Albert-Laszlo Barabasi
# For details see Section 2.1 of the SOM
# Column 2: number of all associated genes
# Column 3: size of the largest connected component (LCC)
# Column 4: significance of the LCC size (z-score)
autoimmune diseases of the nervous system
congenital, hereditary, and neonatal diseases and abnormalities
female urogenital diseases and pregnancy complications
